//Previous surgery


Given	I'm logged-in with valid credentials
And	I'm on Page 02 - Anamnesis of Knee MRI


When I select 'Ligament reconstruction' checkbox
Then 'Anterior cruciate ligament' checkbox is enabled
And 'Medial collateral ligament' checkbox is enabled
And 'Lateral collateral ligament' checkbox is enabled
And 'Posterior cruciate ligament' checkbox is enabled


When I select 'Osteosynthesis' checkbox
Then 'Intramedullary nailing osteosynthesis' checkbox is enabled


When I select 'Cartilage transplantation' checkbox
Then 'Autologous matrix-induced chondrogenesis (AMIC)' radio button is enabled
And 'Autologous chondrocyte transplantation (ACT)' radio button is enabled


When I select 'Meniscus surgery' checkbox
Then 'Resection' checkbox is enabled
And 'Suture' checkbox is enabled

When I select 'Resection' checkbox
Then a multiple Localizer is enabled
When I select 'IMVH' part on the Localizer
Then 'IMVH' is selected and turns red
When I select 'IMPI' part on the Localizer
Then 'IMPI' is selected and turns red

When I select 'Suture' checkbox
Then a multiple Localizer is enabled
When I select 'AMVH' part on the Localizer
Then 'AMVH' is selected and turns red
When I select 'AMPI' part on the Localizer
Then 'AMPI' is selected and turns red
